author: The Wall Street Journal
description:
Guest co-host Miriam Gottfried and Adrienne Yih, senior retail analyst at Barclays, are set to dive into the impact of tariffs on companies such as American Eagle Outfitters, Gap and Abercrombie & Fitch. Then, Yih tells Miriam why this back-to-school season is important for apparel retailers.

title: How Back-to-School Shopping Influences Retailers and Consumers
